Title: Woven
Writer: Ryan Spahn, Salome Mulugeta, Kristin Hanggi
Actors: Salome Mulugeta, Ryan O'Nan, Ryan Spahn, Larisa Polonsky
Plot: Ethiopian-born Elenie struggles to integrate her mother's traditions with her own American dreams. When a tragic accident thrusts her into the life of American-born Logan, Elenie realizes that one's search for a sense of place is universal.
